txt.en: Viznak is tied to an altar. Infected Orcs chant over him
'You save me from crazy Orcs?! Wow, you strong! I go back to hideout, meet you there!'
'Let me go, stupid Orcs! I'll stab you in the eye when I get free!'

Rhadrog's condition grows worse, and the Ranger's medical supplies have failed. Your last option to try and save Rhadrog's life is to hope that the goblin Viznak, wasn't lying when he said he knew how to cure the disease. But where is Viznak?
'You dare steal from The Lady of Blight?'
TBD Rescue Gob-kid from Infested Orcs
Viznak is free and has returned to his hideout.\n\nYou should talk to Viznak.
Viznak the goblin is being held somewhere in the infected Orc village of Faltor Gâm.\n\nYou should find Viznak.
Viznak has been found in the Orc village of Faltor Gâm, tied to an altar.\n\nYou should help Viznak escape the altar.
Viznak has been found in the Orc village of Faltor Gâm, tied to an altar.\n\nYou should rescue Viznak by defeating Ulúrilz!
'You guys strong. That good because Agarnaith will chew you up and spit you out if you not. You made good choice savin' me. Gonna make it up to you!'

'Forced to follow that offensive goblin's trail once again! If Kingsfoil cannot cure this blight, our last hope is to trust his word. We must seek him out and put a stop to this illness. Perhaps he was taken to the north, where I spotted a gathering of those plague-ridden Orcs. Please take care as I must remain here with Rhadrog. Your vigilance will serve you well against Orcs as volatile as those stalking this swamp!'
